Release 0.6.0

New features:
* Split operator into two binaries/containers - operator and monitor
* Timeout to Clickhouse connection
* ActionPlan and .chi.status with progress reports on CHI create/update
* Default namespace to watch in in case no specified explicitly
* ClickHouseInstallationTemplate CRD
* ClickHouseOperatorConfiguration CRD

Improvements:
* Introduce ConfigurationManager
* Enhance multi-thread support for concurrent operations
* Clarify docs and examples
* Unify "CHI add" and "CHI update" execution paths

Bug fixes:

